TY  - JOUR
T1  - Note—Comments on a Queueing Inequality
AU  - Heyman, Daniel P.
Y1  - 1980/09/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.26.9.956
